<div class="seasonal">
  <h1 class="seasonH1">2024 Super Strokers Seasonal Standings</h1>
  <div class="leaderboard">
    <ul class="listOfPlayers">
      <li class="playerRows">Players</li>
      <% players.forEach(function(user, index) { %>
      <li class="playerRows"><%= user.name %></li>
      <% }) %>
    </ul>
    <ul class="holeHolder">
      <% for(i=1; i<=54; i++) { %>
      <li class="hole"><%= i %></li>
      <% } %> <% players.forEach(function(user, index) { %> <% for(i=0; i < 54 ;
      i++) { %> <% if(i < user.scores.length) { %>
      <li class="hole"><%= user.scores[i] %></li>
      <% } else { %>
      <li class="hole">-</li>
      <% }}}) %>
    </ul>
    <ul class="textBox">
      <li class="total">Total</li>
      <% players.forEach(function(user, index) { %>
      <li class="totalities"><%= user.total %></li>
      <%}) %>
    </ul>
    <ul class="textBox2">
      <li class="total2">Thru</li>
      <% players.forEach(function(user, index) { %>
      <li class="totalities2"><%= user.thru %></li>
      <%}) %>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="forms">
    <button class="btn btn-primary" id="addUser">Register</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" id="addScore">Add Round</button>
  </div>
  <div class="rulesSection">
    <h1>Season Rules:</h1>
    <ul class="rules">
      <li class="rule">
        <strong>-</strong> To ensure the validity of scores, all tournament
        rounds must be played alongside at least one other registered member of
        the tournament. This requirement ensures fair play and integrity in the
        scoring process.
      </li>
      <li class="rule">
        <strong>-</strong> Participants are granted the privilege to make minor
        adjustments to their lie, allowing them to move the ball a limited
        distance, typically a couple of inches, to provide better positioning or
        alleviate an unfavorable lie. This allowance contributes to maintaining
        the integrity of the game while providing players with reasonable
        latitude to address challenging circumstances.
      </li>
      <li class="rule">
        <strong>-</strong> Each participant is entitled to utilize one mulligan
        per nine-hole segment of the tournament. A mulligan affords the player
        the opportunity to retake a shot of their choice, thereby mitigating the
        impact of an undesirable outcome on their overall score. This provision
        aims to promote fairness and mitigate the effects of occasional missteps
        during play.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <form action="/addUser" method="POST" id="form" class="display-none">
    <div class="exitOut">X</div>
    <label for="name">Name:</label>
    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" />
    <label>Password:</label>
    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="password" name="password" />
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
  </form>
  <form action="/addScores" method="POST" id="scores" class="display-none">
    <div class="exitOut" id="option2">X</div>
    <ul class="roundInput">
      <li class="inputHole">
        <label for="one" class="holeInput">1</label>
        <input type="number" name="one" id="one" class="inputScore" />
      </li>
      <li class="inputHole">
        <label for="two" class="holeInput">2</label>
        <input type="number" name="two" id="two" class="inputScore" />
      </li>
      <li class="inputHole">
        <label for="three" class="holeInput">3</label>
        <input type="number" name="three" id="three" class="inputScore" />
      </li>
      <li class="inputHole">
        <label for="four" class="holeInput">4</label>
        <input type="number" name="four" id="four" class="inputScore" />
      </li>
      <li class="inputHole">
        <label for="five" class="holeInput">5</label>
        <input type="number" name="five" id="five" class="inputScore" />
      </li>
      <li class="inputHole">
        <label for="six" class="holeInput">6</label>
        <input type="number" name="six" id="six" class="inputScore" />
      </li>
      <li class="inputHole">
        <label for="seven" class="holeInput">7</label>
        <input type="number" name="seven" id="seven" class="inputScore" />
      </li>
      <li class="inputHole">
        <label for="eight" class="holeInput">8</label>
        <input type="number" name="eight" id="eight" class="inputScore" />
      </li>
      <li class="inputHole">
        <label for="nine" class="holeInput">9</label>
        <input type="number" name="nine" id="nine" class="inputScore" />
      </li>
    </ul>
    <label>Password:</label>
    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="password2" name="password2" />
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
  </form>
</div>
